Text:
I just wanted to thank you for this wonderful gift to earth residents!

This is a massive project, just want you to know that your hard work and dedication is appreciated by many, many people who are too shy to register and say so! :)

Thank you Blueboy for taking all this trouble to preserve TV history. Several of the episodes you uploaded earlier have run dry of seeders and stand still at 90%. Hope you can take a few minutes and seed them again up to 100%.
